data.description: 29 + ACRES!!! Dreaming of Barndominium living? We have got the perfect place for you! Set up perfectly for a horse training &/or a horse boarding facility. Spacious rooms and offering 2 full kitchens & 2 living areas. attached. On these cold winter days, you will enjoy your 2 fireplaces. One is a wood burning free standing fireplace, & the 2nd is a wood pellet / corn burning fireplace. Beautiful claw foot bathtub to relax in after a long day at work. Hand painted horse murals on the pocket doors. No need to worry about power outages. Home is equipped with a whole house propane generator. 2 Central Electric Air Conditioning systems. Matching 24' x 60' Equipment / Loafing Building could easily be converted into additional barn space or convert into additional horse stalls. The 29+ ACRES is fenced & cross fenced for your livestock. Includes underground water lines, estimated 7+ outdoor water hydrants where water is run out in the pasture(s) for easy watering. Livestock shelters in place. Barn is attached to the house has concrete flooring, tack area, feed area, indoor shower that could also convert to an indoor wash rack for your horse(s). Outdoor horse wash rack in place. The property has a chicken coop, & a greenhouse equipped with water and electric. The entrance to this property is gated which maximizes privacy. Hike to the back part of the land to see plenty of wildlife including deer & wild turkey makes your own personal hunting spot. This property is ready for its new owners to make a lifetime of memories with!
